summary: This document appears to be a financial agreement related to an auto bill payment service for a mortgage loan with Fifth Third Mortgage. It outlines the terms of the agreement, including payment initiation and conditions for cancellation.
keyFacts: The document is related to an auto bill payment service for a mortgage loan.
The total payment amount specified is $2,244.39.
There is a requirement to maintain payments for one year from the closing date of the loan.
Cancellation of the Auto BillPayer service prior to one year incurs a fee of $1,625.
